text: Chen Ta-ching (; 1904–1973) was a Kuomintang general from Jiangxi, Republic of China. Chen was the Governor of Taiwan Province from 1969 to 1972 and the Minister of Defense from 1972 to 1973. |- Category:1904 births Category:1973 deaths Category:National Revolutionary Army generals from Jiangxi Category:Politicians from Ganzhou Category:Republic of China politicians from Jiangxi Category:Chairpersons of the Taiwan Provincial Government Category:Taiwanese Ministers of National Defense Category:Taiwanese people from Jiangxi Category:Republic of China people born during Qing
